    "body": "I think this comes from ethers. See [this issue](https://github.com/ethers-io/ethers.js/issues/2982). This was working before because both us and ethers were going together against the spec :sweat_smile:\r\n\r\nBy the way, we recently released a new package (in beta) to help with things like these. If anyone is interested in trying it, check [this doc](https://nomiclabs.notion.site/Public-Hardhat-Network-Helpers-216cf3c665124895bf1f6e2f9343f86f).\r\n\r\nI'm going to close this issue now since there's not much we can do on our side.",
